SUMMARY:Nirbhay Nirgun
DESCRIPTION:‘Nirbhay Nirgun Gun Re Gaunga\,’ Kabir wrote. \nThe fearless\, nirbhay\, and the formless\, nirgun: this is the aspiration for the mind. \nNirbhay Nirgun is a concert celebrating Kabir’s philosophy and his plain-spoken wisdom through song\, interspersed with discussion that contextualises the verses within today’s challenging socio-political climate. Hindustani classical musicians Nimish and Avanti bring this journey to life through some of Kabir’s most iconic writing — settings immortalised by Kumar Gandharva and Madhup Mudgal\, compositions by their guru Padma Shri Dr Ashwini Bhide Deshpande\, and new compositions by Nimish himself. \nKahat Kabir Suno Bhai Sadho\, Jeet Nishan Ghuraunga! \nCredits\nWriter- Avanti Patel\nVocals- Avanti Patel & Nimish Kaikadi\nTabla- Vighnesh Kamath\nHarmonium- Vishvajith Kini\nPercussions- Shamdath Ravi \nSupported by: \n \n  \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/nirbhay-nirgun/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Music,Performing Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Thumbnail-3.jpg
END:VEVENT
